{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "8b51d8b4-05d6-4eb2-a083-fca6f047ff6f",
		"name": "User Auth & Admin API Collection",
		"description": "Comprehensive Postman collection for the MongoDB-backed Node.js Express User Authentication, User Management, Activity Log, and Image Moderation APIs.\n\n### Collection Variables\n- **base_url**: The host address (e.g. `http://localhost:5000`).\n- **token**: Holds the JWT session token (automatically set upon Register, Login, or Reset Password).\n- **otp**: Holds the 6-digit OTP code (automatically set upon requesting a forgot password in non-production environments).\n- **user_id**: Target user ID for user management endpoints.\n- **image_id**: Target image ID for image moderation/deletion endpoints.\n- **temp_token**: Temporary token for completing 2FA login verification.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
